      "content": "it's not just about healing though. that person was the only reason any of this mattered. i look in the mirror and it's like looking at a stranger. there's no point in trying to \"fix\" something that's fundamentally broken and gone. i feel like i'm just a shell waiting for the rest to catch up.",
